<p dir=3D"auto">State-of-the-art language models can match human performanc=
e on many tasks, but they still struggle to robustly perform multi-step mat=
hematical reasoning. To diagnose the failures of current models and support=
 research, we're releasing GSM8K, a dataset of 8.5K high quality linguistic=
ally diverse grade school math word problems. We find that even the largest=
 transformer models fail to achieve high test performance, despite the conc=
eptual simplicity of this problem distribution.</p>
<p align=3D"center" dir=3D"auto">
    <a target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://github=
.com/openai/grade-school-math/blob/master/grade_school_math/img/example_pro=
blems.png"><img src=3D"https://github.com/openai/grade-school-math/raw/mast=
er/grade_school_math/img/example_problems.png" height=3D"300" style=3D"max-=
width: 100%;"></a>
</p>
<div class=3D"markdown-heading" dir=3D"auto"><h2 tabindex=3D"-1" class=3D"h=
eading-element" dir=3D"auto">Dataset Details</h2><a id=3D"user-content-data=
